				label(for="apem" class="col-form-label col-sm-2") Apellido Materno:
				.col-sm-auto
					input(type="text" class="form-control" id="apem" name="apem" placeholder="Apellido Materno")
				label(for="ci" class="col-form-label col-sm-2") C.I:
				.col-sm-auto
					input(type="text" class="form-control " id="id_ci" name="ci" placeholder="CI" onkeypress="ValidaSoloNumeros();")
			.form-group.row
				label(for="dir" class="col-form-label col-sm-2") Direccion:
